data.description: Stop the car!! New lower pricing!! Spectacular views across this 29-acre lake are just one of the features of this turnkey furnished villa. With 9ft ceilings and an extra window in the living room area gives a bright and airy feel and a lanai to relax with a beer or cocktail. The kitchen has a convection oven, bright and light backsplash and is roomy with plenty of storage with lower cabinets, pull out shelves with soft close drawers plus an additional pantry. All of the carpeting has been removed, with either luxury vinyl or tile as the preferred choice. The master bedroom with ensuite bathroom overlooks the lake, so you wake every morning to the lakeview with birds and turtles. A separate office/bedroom with closet gives you options for workspace or art room etc. The second bedroom has plenty of space for family or friends to visit and a 2-car garage complete this beautiful home. Close to everything that Punta Gorda has to offer including the new Pickle-plex. So, pack your suitcase and toothbrush to make this your ' Piece of Paradise".
